platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Put your to-dos in TickTick, and boom: They’re all in perfect order. This all-in-one organizer is a personal assistant for your brain, one that eases the mental strain of All That Stuff To Do by elegantly organizing it, which lets you focus less on deadlines and more on the big picture. Put it right to work as a refined (and visually pleasing) to-do list, or make use of power features like its Eisenhower Matrix, which automatically plots your tasks on a chart in terms of urgency and importance, or the built-in Pomodoro timer, which keeps you properly balanced between productivity and burnout. “People don’t just want a task manager,” says founder Damon Woo. “They want to manage everything in their lives.”
改進你的待辦事項列表，在圖表上確定工作任務的優先順序，或使用內置的番茄計時器，讓你在工作效率和休息之間保持平衡。
解放大脑，让生活更轻松。优化待办事项清单，为任务设置优先级，使用番茄计时保持专注，或是设置特殊日期提醒，每项操作都得心应手，时间管理更高效。
あなたの日常生活を整理するのに役立つアプリです。ToDoリストを整理し、表を使ってタスクに優先順位をつけ、付属のポモドーロタイマーで仕事の効率を上げながら、燃え尽きないようにバランスを保ちましょう。
A personal assistant for your brain. Refine your to-do list, prioritise your tasks on a chart or use the built-in Pomodoro timer to keep you balanced between productivity and burnout.
